#: ../learn_more.rst:23
msgid "Learn More"
msgstr "了解更多"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:24
msgid ""
"We are working hard to expand this user guide and to improve OpenShot Video "
"Editor, but if you are stuck and don't know where to turn, OpenShot has "
"several sources for additional information."
msgstr ""
"我们正在努力扩展本用户指南并改进 OpenShot Video Editor，但如果您遇到困难，不知道该向哪里求助，OpenShot "
"提供了多个额外信息来源。"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:27
msgid ""
"OpenShot has several `YouTube Tutorials "
"<https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLymupH2aoNQNezYzv2lhSwvoyZgLp1Q0T>`_"
" available to help you learn more."
msgstr ""
"OpenShot 提供了多个 `YouTube 教程 "
"<https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLymupH2aoNQNezYzv2lhSwvoyZgLp1Q0T>`_"
" ，帮助您深入学习。 `YouTube Tutorials "
"<https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLymupH2aoNQNezYzv2lhSwvoyZgLp1Q0T>`_"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:28
msgid ""
"OpenShot has a `Reddit User Community <https://openshot.org/forum>`_ "
"dedicated to users helping users, answering questions, and discussing video "
"editing and OpenShot topics."
msgstr ""
"OpenShot 拥有一个 `Reddit 用户社区 <https://openshot.org/forum>`_ "
"，专注于用户互助、解答问题以及讨论视频编辑和 OpenShot 相关话题。 `Reddit User Community "
"<https://openshot.org/forum>`_"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:29
msgid ""
"If you would like to help improve this User Guide, `view source on GitHub "
"<https://github.com/OpenShot/openshot-qt/tree/develop/doc>`_."
msgstr ""
"如果您愿意帮助改进本用户指南，请 `在 GitHub 查看源代码 <https://github.com/OpenShot/openshot-"
"qt/tree/develop/doc>`_ 。 `view source on GitHub "
"<https://github.com/OpenShot/openshot-qt/tree/develop/doc>`_"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:30
msgid ""
"If you have discovered a new bug, please `Report a Bug "
"<https://www.openshot.org/issues/new/>`_."
msgstr ""
"如果您发现了新错误，请 `报告错误 <https://www.openshot.org/issues/new/>`_ 。 `Report a Bug "
"<https://www.openshot.org/issues/new/>`_"

# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../learn_more.rst:31
msgid ""
"If you need professional support, you can open a ticket by sending an "
"message to support@openshot.org or `Schedule a call "
"<https://calendly.com/openshot-support/desktop>`_."
msgstr ""
"如果您需要专业支持，可以发送邮件至 support@openshot.org 开启工单，或 `预约电话支持 "
"<https://calendly.com/openshot-support/desktop>`_ 。 `Schedule a call "
"<https://calendly.com/openshot-support/desktop>`_"
